---
title: Alex Tran
overrideBaseTitle: true
layout: layouts/base.njk
---

<div class="homepage-content center stack gap-xl" style="--center-max: 65ch; padding-block: var(--s3)">
    {# Hero #}
    <header class="stack gap-sm">
        <!--<p class="text-lg color-muted">*shrug*</p>-->
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Howdy, here are the relevant bits ...</h1>
    </header>

    {# Bio Box #}
    <section class="intro-box stack gap-md">
        <p class="text-lg leading-tight">
            I'm a developer and writer who cares about building things that last.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Building developer tools and thinking about software craft</li>
            <li>Previously shipped products at Stripe and Google</li>
            <li>Based in San Francisco, originally from Vietnam</li>
            <li>Writing here about technology, design, and the creative process</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    {# Featured Posts #}
    <section class="stack gap-md">
        <h2 class="text-base uppercase font-medium section-heading font-base" data-weight="medium">Featured</h2>
        <div class="stack" style="--stack-space: 0">
            {%- for post in collections.featured %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-link">
                <div class="post-title text-lg font-medium font-heading leading-extra-tight">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
                <div class="post-desc color-muted">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
            </a>
            {%- endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>

    {# Recent Posts #}
    {%- set remainingPosts = collections.posts | reverse | length - 3 %}
    {%- if remainingPosts > 0 %}
    <section class="stack gap-md">
        <h2 class="text-base uppercase font-medium section-heading font-base" data-weight="thin">Latest</h2>
        <div class="stack" style="--stack-space: 0">
            {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-link">
                <div class="post-title font-medium font-heading leading-extra-tight">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
                <div class="post-desc text-smed color-muted">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
            </a>
            {%- endfor %}
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/" class="color-primary width-fit">See all posts</a>
    </section>
    {%- endif %}
</div>
